# Cursor Project Instructions

## First Steps

**READ THE README.md FIRST.** It contains essential documentation about:
- Project structure and file organization
- Component patterns and the `locale` prop system
- i18n system and translation files
- SEO configuration (files marked with `// SEO:` comments)
- ContentForge API integration
- Tailwind styling conventions

## Project Overview

Landing page template for conversion-focused marketing sites:
- Single-language (French) or bilingual (French/English) via `ENABLE_MULTILANG` env var
- ContentForge API for dynamic FAQ content
- Complete SEO (Open Graph, JSON-LD, hreflang, sitemap)

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/site.config.ts` | SEO: Site metadata, contact, social |
| `astro.config.mjs` | SEO: Site URL and base path |
| `src/i18n/locales/*.json` | All translatable text content |
| `src/layouts/Layout.astro` | SEO: Meta tags, hreflang, JSON-LD |
| `src/lib/seo.ts` | JSON-LD builders |
| `src/lib/contentforge.ts` | API integration |

## Component Pattern

All components accept `locale: Locale` prop and use `getFixedT(locale)` for translations:

```astro
---
import { getFixedT, type Locale } from '../i18n/i18n';

interface Props {
  locale: Locale;
}

const { locale } = Astro.props;
const t = getFixedT(locale);
---
```

## Tailwind CSS — STRICT RULES

### ✅ ALWAYS: Native Tailwind Classes Only

```astro
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4">
<button class="rounded-lg bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700">
```

### ❌ NEVER: Arbitrary Values (Brackets)

```astro
<!-- FORBIDDEN -->
<div class="w-[347px] text-[#1a2b3c]">
```

### ❌ NEVER: Inline Styles

```astro
<!-- FORBIDDEN -->
<div style="margin: 23px;">
```

### Animation Priority

1. Native Tailwind: `animate-pulse`, `animate-spin`, `animate-bounce`
2. Transitions: `transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-emerald-700`
3. Keyframes in `global.css`: Only if explicitly requested

## SEO Markers

Look for `// SEO:` comments in code — these indicate elements requiring updates for SEO setup.

## i18n Guidelines

- All user-facing text uses `t('Key.subkey')` translation function
- Keys organized by component in `src/i18n/locales/fr.json` and `en.json`
- Component/variable names stay in English

## Conversion Focus

- Guide visitors toward clear conversion actions
- Primary CTA: `bg-emerald-600 text-white hover:bg-emerald-700`
- Secondary CTA: `border border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50`

## Color Palette

- Primary: `emerald-600`, `emerald-700`
- Dark: `gray-900`, `gray-950`
- Light: `white`, `gray-50`
- Text: `gray-900` (headings), `gray-600` (body)
- Borders: `gray-200`, `gray-300`
